  dialogueLines:
  - <emotion=happy>Hey! Good to see you!
  - I've been thinking<pause=0.1> about what you said.
  - <emotion=nervous>And, uh... I might have messed up.
  - <speed=15><emotion=defeated>I accidentally sold the car for way too little.
  - <emotion=angry>Before you say anything, YES I know it was stupid.
  - <emotion=stretch>Anyway... <emotion=dismiss>what's done is done.
  - <speed=30><emotion=happy>Let's grab a drink and forget about it!
